<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 04:10:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人质谈判的假象已经过时，以色列和哈马斯都不想让步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/the-hostage-talks-facade-is-wearing-out-and-neither-israel-or-hamas-want-to-budge/00000191-9f49-d172-abd9-ffdf9e840000</link><description>上周发生的所有严峻而动荡的事件并没有改变任何事情：停火谈判毫无进展，因为此时达成的协议对内塔尼亚胡或辛瓦尔没有好处。仪式失败继续发生</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 03:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/the-hostage-talks-facade-is-wearing-out-and-neither-israel-or-hamas-want-to-budge/00000191-9f49-d172-abd9-ffdf9e840000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的谎言被揭穿：以色列如何忽视 10 月 7 日灾难的路线图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-lies-laid-bare-how-israel-ignored-the-roadmap-to-the-october-7-disaster/00000191-9fbc-d453-ab9f-ffbc6ec50000</link><description>反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德 (Yair Lapid) 在民事调查小组中的证词描绘了一幅可怕的画面 ■ 总理再次修改了自己的简历，但无意中认罪了 ■ 没有人知道他是否支持米里·雷格夫 (Miri Regev) 10 月 7 日纪念仪式的计划 ■ 那是什么？ Yair Golan 没听懂？</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-lies-laid-bare-how-israel-ignored-the-roadmap-to-the-october-7-disaster/00000191-9fbc-d453-ab9f-ffbc6ec50000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：以色列内阁批准以色列国防军继续沿有争议的加沙边境路线驻军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article-live/source-israeli-cabinet-okays-continued-idf-presence-along-contentious-gaza-border-route/00000191-a11f-df21-a9b9-b31fe2310000</link><description>世界卫生组织高级官员表示，以色列军队同意在加沙暂停人道主义行动，以开展脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种行动。 联合国监督机构称，伊朗进一步增加浓缩铀库存，达到接近武器级水平。犯罪事件 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部称，过去一天约旦河西岸有 16 人死亡 ■ 法国总统马克龙、英国首相斯塔默重申呼吁“立即停火”</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 02:49:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article-live/source-israeli-cabinet-okays-continued-idf-presence-along-contentious-gaza-border-route/00000191-a11f-df21-a9b9-b31fe2310000</guid></item><item><title>卡玛拉·哈里斯告诉美国有线电视新闻网：我不会接受拜登的以色列政策。我们必须完成停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/harris-tells-cnn-no-change-in-bidens-israel-policy-we-have-to-get-cease-fire-deal-done/00000191-a0fd-d172-abd9-eaff68f80001</link><description>在作为 2024 年民主党总统候选人首次接受采访时，副总统重申了她的信念，即“以色列有权保卫自己”，但补充说“如何做到这一点很重要”</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 02:04:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/harris-tells-cnn-no-change-in-bidens-israel-policy-we-have-to-get-cease-fire-deal-done/00000191-a0fd-d172-abd9-eaff68f80001</guid></item><item><title>以色列最后的、脆弱的反腐败堡垒即将倒塌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/final-bulwark-against-corruption-is-about-to-fall/00000191-9fbb-d0ae-af93-ffffb7b30000</link><description>过去几年对反腐败战争不利，让本-格维尔任命警察调查部门的下一任负责人将对其造成致命打击。然后是内塔尼亚胡，他寻求完全接管公务员制度</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 22:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/final-bulwark-against-corruption-is-about-to-fall/00000191-9fbb-d0ae-af93-ffffb7b30000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普最高外交政策顾问警告：如果英国停止向以色列出售武器，特殊关系将面临风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/trumps-foreign-policy-aide-special-relationship-at-risk-if-uk-halts-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-a02d-d453-ab9f-f8ad6aa20000</link><description>罗伯特·奥布莱恩（Robert O&amp;#39;Brien）在接受伦敦政策交流智囊团采访时表示，如果特朗普11月获胜，他可能会进入特朗普内阁，英国的武器禁运“将真正伤害西方联盟和北约”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 22:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/trumps-foreign-policy-aide-special-relationship-at-risk-if-uk-halts-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-a02d-d453-ab9f-f8ad6aa20000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：以色列司法部长威胁要改变主要司法委员会的组成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/sources-israeli-justice-minister-threatens-to-change-makeup-of-key-judicial-committee/00000191-9fbd-d172-abd9-ffbf26e90000</link><description>据报道，亚里夫·莱文告诉代理首席大法官，如果他的最高法院候选人未获批准，他和其他部长也将加紧努力罢免以色列总检察长</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 21:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/sources-israeli-justice-minister-threatens-to-change-makeup-of-key-judicial-committee/00000191-9fbd-d172-abd9-ffbf26e90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列跆拳道运动员阿萨夫·亚苏尔 (Asaf Yasur) 在 2024 年巴黎残奥会上获得金牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-taekwondo-athlete-asaf-yasur-takes-gold-medal-in-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-9fa3-d0ae-af93-ffff75260000</link><description>22岁的亚苏尔在男子残疾人跆拳道比赛中排名世界第一，并且是两届世界冠军。他在男子-58公斤级比赛中击败了世界排名第二的土耳其选手阿里·坎·奥兹坎，为以色列赢得了第385枚残奥会奖牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 20:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-taekwondo-athlete-asaf-yasur-takes-gold-medal-in-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-9fa3-d0ae-af93-ffff75260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称哈马斯伪造加沙战争民意调查结果以夸大公众支持率</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-says-hamas-falsified-gaza-war-poll-results-to-exaggerate-public-support/00000191-9f6a-d794-a7f5-dffb5ce90000</link><description>以色列国防军声称，它发现了一些文件，揭示了哈马斯如何操纵受人尊敬的巴勒斯坦民意调查来抬高哈马斯的支持率。民意调查专家哈利勒·希卡基 (Khalil Shikaki) 回应道：“这听起来像是[以色列]军队和哈马斯之间为了塑造公众舆论而进行的一场叙事战争”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 19:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-says-hamas-falsified-gaza-war-poll-results-to-exaggerate-public-support/00000191-9f6a-d794-a7f5-dffb5ce90000</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织官员称以色列军方同意加沙人道主义暂停以进行脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/who-official-says-israeli-military-agrees-to-gaza-humanitarian-pauses-for-polio-shots/00000191-9f36-d0ae-af93-ffff9d430000</link><description>以色列军方支持短暂停火，但正在等待政府做出决定，允许在加沙出现首例小儿麻痹症后为 60 万名儿童接种疫苗</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 18:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/who-official-says-israeli-military-agrees-to-gaza-humanitarian-pauses-for-polio-shots/00000191-9f36-d0ae-af93-ffff9d430000</guid></item><item><title>帮助和教唆犹太定居者的恐怖活动：现在会产生真正的后果吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/aiding-and-abetting-jewish-settler-terror-will-there-now-be-real-consequences/00000191-9ecc-d453-ab9f-feccc2f20000</link><description>以色列军队高层承认定居者的暴力行为，并称其为恐怖主义行为。现在，它必须对允许和教唆这些犯罪的士兵实施与对平民相同的处罚</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 18:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/aiding-and-abetting-jewish-settler-terror-will-there-now-be-real-consequences/00000191-9ecc-d453-ab9f-feccc2f20000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高级外交官博雷尔谈以色列、内塔尼亚胡和加沙战争：“以色列自卫的权利是有限度的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-to-self-defense-has-a-limit-top-eu-diplomat-on-netanyahu-settlers-gaza/00000191-9e18-d453-ab9f-fe9cfc570000</link><description>欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔对欧盟在帮助加沙人民、建设中东和平以及遏制内塔尼亚胡政府中的极端分子方面做得不够感到沮丧。他在接受《国土报》采访时表示，“往好了说，我们是被动的，往坏了说是被动的，当然没有我们应有的积极主动性”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 18:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-to-self-defense-has-a-limit-top-eu-diplomat-on-netanyahu-settlers-gaza/00000191-9e18-d453-ab9f-fe9cfc570000</guid></item><item><title>谷歌曝光的伊朗针对以色列合作者的反情报行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/iranian-counter-intelligence-operation-targeting-israeli-collaborators-exposed-by-google/00000191-9f00-d453-ab9f-ff8cee220000</link><description>多年来，具有安全背景、讲阿拉伯语和波斯语的虚假职位列表一直在网上发布，显然是为了欺骗潜在的合作者；活动与 Shin Bet 透露的活动几乎相同</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/iranian-counter-intelligence-operation-targeting-israeli-collaborators-exposed-by-google/00000191-9f00-d453-ab9f-ff8cee220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高中工会因与财政部发生纠纷而宣布罢工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-school-union-announces-strike-amid-disputes-with-finance-ministry/00000191-9eb8-d172-abd9-febfaecc0000</link><description>以色列中学教师协会表示，财政部正在“不惜一切代价试图打破有组织的劳工，将教育系统私有化，并与教师签订个人合同，从而将他们变成合同工”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:29:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-school-union-announces-strike-amid-disputes-with-finance-ministry/00000191-9eb8-d172-abd9-febfaecc0000</guid></item><item><title>我为什么要离开以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-i-am-leaving-israel/00000191-9dc7-d314-a9f5-9df7403e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:29:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-i-am-leaving-israel/00000191-9dc7-d314-a9f5-9df7403e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 328 天：世卫组织官员称，以色列国防军同意暂停加沙脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-328-idf-agreed-to-gaza-pauses-for-polio-vaccination-who-official-says/00000191-9ec7-d453-ab9f-fecfd5d00000</link><description>获救的人质凯德·法尔汉·卡迪表示，以色列人质阿尔耶·扎尔马诺维奇在哈马斯囚禁期间因缺乏医疗救治而死亡。 美国、埃及和卡塔尔预计将在“几天内”提出新提案，以解决停战谈判中的两个关键问题 欧盟的外交政策酋长正式询问成员国是否要考虑制裁“一些以色列部长”煽动反巴勒斯坦行为 ■ 这是战争开始 328 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-328-idf-agreed-to-gaza-pauses-for-polio-vaccination-who-official-says/00000191-9ec7-d453-ab9f-fecfd5d00000</guid></item><item><title>2024 年巴黎残奥会：值得关注的以色列运动员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article-timeline/.premium/paris-2024-paralympics-the-israeli-athletes-to-look-out-for/00000191-9ed3-d314-a9f5-9ff3ca030000</link><description>以色列能否在 2020 年东京奥运会上夺得 9 枚奖牌？游泳、跆拳道、赛艇、网球和女子门球等项目的杰出选手很有可能在巴黎奥运会上取得好成绩</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:26:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article-timeline/.premium/paris-2024-paralympics-the-israeli-athletes-to-look-out-for/00000191-9ed3-d314-a9f5-9ff3ca030000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫市政府表示公共游泳池已关闭，为极端正统派开放，并实行性别隔离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-said-public-pool-was-closed-opened-it-for-ultra-orthodox-with-gender-segregation/00000191-9eb3-d453-ab9f-febf91990000</link><description>本月，一个市政游泳池在性别隔离的情况下悄然运营了几天，通过市政府的托拉文化部门提供打折门票，而市政府则隐瞒了该项目预算的详细信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-said-public-pool-was-closed-opened-it-for-ultra-orthodox-with-gender-segregation/00000191-9eb3-d453-ab9f-febf91990000</guid></item><item><title>“我希望有人付钱给我，我会和他住在一起，每个星期天我都会为他写弥撒。就是这样&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-someone-to-pay-me-ill-live-with-him-and-every-sunday-ill-write-a-mass-for-him/00000191-9ea1-d172-abd9-feb73a470000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名年轻的以色列妇女与她的父亲一起飞往哥本哈根以获得外国公民身份，另一名妇女准备与她的双胞胎妹妹一起从军</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-someone-to-pay-me-ill-live-with-him-and-every-sunday-ill-write-a-mass-for-him/00000191-9ea1-d172-abd9-feb73a470000</guid></item><item><title>新报告称，到 2023 年，纽约 44% 的仇恨犯罪都是以犹太人为目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/jews-were-target-of-44-percent-of-all-hate-crimes-in-new-york-in-2023-says-new-report/00000191-9e37-d18a-a1b7-bf378fed0000</link><description>纽约州审计长的一份新报告显示，纽约市所有重罪仇恨犯罪中有 65% 是针对犹太人的，而且越来越多的攻击针对的是人而不是财产</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:32:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/jews-were-target-of-44-percent-of-all-hate-crimes-in-new-york-in-2023-says-new-report/00000191-9e37-d18a-a1b7-bf378fed0000</guid></item></channel></rss>